==竞赛规程==
参加本届赛事的16支球队被分成2个小组，每个小组的前4名将晋级淘汰赛。 <ref name="Format2014">{{cite web| title = Information| url = http://www.iihfworlds2015.com/en/information/| publisher = IIHF| accessdate = 6 April 2015| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150407200615/http://www.iihfworlds2015.com/en/information/| archive-date = 2015-04-07| dead-url = yes}}</ref>

小组赛的积分规则如下：
*常规时间获胜的球队得到3分 ('''W''')。
*在加时赛或互射罚球中获胜的球队获得2分。加时赛时长3分钟，为金球制胜制。如果在加时赛中双方都不能进球，那么比赛进入互射罚球阶段。在淘汰赛阶段，加时赛时长变为10分钟；在决赛，加时赛时长变为20分钟。 (GWS) ('''OTW''')。<ref name="Format2014"/> Game Winning Shots procedure is as follows: Three different players from each team would take alternate shots. If the game is still tied after this, one player from each team would take alternating shots until one scored and the other missed. Only the decisive goal counted in the result table for group play.<ref name="Format2014"/>|group=n}}
*在加时赛或互射罚球中落败的球队获得1分 ('''OTL''')。
*在常规时间落败的球队得0分 ('''L''')。
如果小组中有2支或以上的球队积分相同，由以下的方式决定排名:<ref name="Format2014"/>
